Package oop.simplebankapp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    The Account class is an abstract representation of a bank account.
    Bank
    The Bank class is an abstract representation of a bank.
    Customer
    The Customer class is an abstract representation of a bank customer.
    DayToDayAccount
    The DayToDayAccount class is a subclass of the Account class.
    PayrollAccount
    The PayrollAccount class is a subclass of the Account class.
    SavingsAccount
    The SavingsAccount class is a subclass of the Account class.
    Validation
    The Validation class contains static methods that perform validation controls on user inputs.
    VirtualAssistant
    The VirtualAssistant class is the driver class of the simple bank app project.
